			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've been saying this for a bit, and I've been encouraged to actually post specific ideas.
<br />
I know about the 'top 10' for mages, and I just thought I'd post a few specifics for what I'd want.  I know I don't have the numbers right or such, but I think it will give you the idea, and I'm not saying these ideas couldn't use work from someone more familiar with the magician class, but I just want to put the ideas out there.  Basically it keeps in the line of magicians being "masters of the elements."
<br />

<br />
Just a few things to keep in mind, the "Spirit" lines don'ts stack with each other, nor do the "Touch" lines, nor do the "Blessing" lines, but the Spirit lines and Touch lines Do stack, as do the Blessing and Touch lines.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Earth Spells:</span>
<br />
Touch of Earth:  Level 8
<br />
   Mana Cost:  100
<br />
   Casting Time:  8
<br />
   Duration:  30m
<br />
   Target:  Group
<br />
   Effect:  Str + 5 (lvl 8) to +30 (lvl 60)
<br />
                AC +10 (lvl 8) to 100 (lvl 60)
<br />
   Restrictions:  ToE does not stack with Temp/Virtue or the Strength line of spells.
<br />

<br />
Spirit of the Earth:  Level 12
<br />
   Mana Cost:  200
<br />
   Casting Time:  12
<br />
   Duration:  40m
<br />
   Target:  Self
<br />
   Effect:  Str + 15 (lvl 12) to +50 (lvl 60)
<br />
                AC +40 (lvl 12) to +250 (lvl 60)
<br />
                DR +20 (lvl 12) to +60 (lvl 60)
<br />
