				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm going to be flamed for this, but I actually like them.  Need reworking, but in general I like the theory.  A couple don't make a whole lot of sense, but as far as the earth and air spells I'm with you.  A knockback+stun AE would actually be kind of nice for those situations when you're screwed and need those extra 5 seconds to gate, not really exploitable because of the truly massive aggro it would cause.  
<br />

<br />
Giving magicians elementally based group benecifial spells would be a nice improvement to the class, albeit one that I would not willingly sacrifice pet strength for.  Yes the stacking issues would be odd, but it's no reason to just dismiss someone's ideas out of hand.  C'mon guys, give him some credit.<br />_________________<br />Dorai Darkspire, 65 Arch Convoker of Maelin Starpyre
